**/ios/Flutter/Generated.xcconfig
**/ios/Flutter/flutter_export_environment.sh
**/ios/Pods/
**/ios/.symlinks/
**/Flutter/App.framework
**/Flutter/Flutter.framework
.metadata

# Melos
.melos_tool/

